### チャンネル更新（名前のみ）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/channels/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "新しいチャンネル名"
}

### チャンネル更新（複数フィールド）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/channels/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "新しいチャンネル名",
  "description": "新しい説明",
  "userPrompt": "新しいスクリプトプロンプト"
}

### チャンネル更新（公開）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/channels/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "publishedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### チャンネル更新（非公開化）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/channels/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "publishedAt": ""
}

### チャンネル削除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/channels/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
